channel.title: I compiled, and no errors, but when I run, this pops up?!
channel.description:
Okay, I moved all my NPC's from edgevil to my new Home site. Compile worked fine, but this came when I ran server:
Exception in thread "main" DiscipleScape Online! Original source: 317 Server Coded by Disciple. java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 7 at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1967) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:548) at server.main(server.java:111)
Any idea whats wrong?
